{
  "_doc": "Phase 2: 16:9 horizontal cover master. Cloned from generate_master_1x1.json with EmptyFlux2LatentImage set to 3840×2160 (Flux2 latent halves to actual 1920 × 1080 (16:9 horizontal cover)).",
  "_inputs_doc": {
